@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Privacy Policy";
}

<!--internal styling-->
<style>
    /* Base Styles */
    .header-container {
        width: 100%;
        height: 40vh;
        display: block;
        background-image: url("/images/about-background.jpg");
        background-size: cover;
        background-repeat: no-repeat;
        color: white;
    }
    .header-container h1 {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 8rem;
    }
    .about-history {
        margin-top: 3rem;
        background-color: white;
        width: 100%;
        height: 60vh; 
        justify-content: center;
        display: flex; 
        flex-wrap: wrap; 
    }
    .about-content {
        background-color: white;
        width: 40%;
        height: 55vh;
        margin: 0 2.5%;
        text-align: center;
    }
    .about-content img {
            width: 100%;
            height: 52vh;
            object-fit: cover;
    }
    .about-content h1 {
            font-size: 28px;
    }
    .about-content p {
            text-align: left;
            padding: 0 15px;
    }
    .founder-container {
        margin-top: 4rem;
        width: 100%;
        height: 70vh; 
        background-color: white;
        justify-content: center;
        display: flex; 
        flex-wrap: wrap; 
    }
    .founder-content {
        width: 40%; 
        height: 70vh;
        background-color: white;
        margin: 0 2.5%;
        text-align: center;
    }
    .founder-content img {
            width: 100%;
            height: 69vh;
            object-fit: cover;
    }
    .founder-content p {
            text-align: left;
            padding: 0 15px;
    }
   .footer-container {
        font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif, 'Roboto Condensed', sans-serif;
        color: white;
        background-color: black;
        width: 100%;
        height: 40vh;
        justify-content: center;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        margin-top: 5rem;
        text-align: center;
        padding: 20px 0;
    }
    .footer-icons {
        display: flex;
        justify-content: center;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 20px;
        font-size: 20px;
    }
    .footer-icons a {
            color: white;
    }
    .footer-icons a:hover i {
                font-size: 25px;
                transition: 0.3s;
                color: red;
    }
    @@media (max-width: 768px) {
    .header-container h1{
        margin-top: 6rem;
        font-size: 36px;
    }
    .about-history {
        flex-direction: column;
        height: auto; 
        margin-top: 1rem;
    }
    .about-content {
        width: 90%;
        height: auto; 
        margin: 15px auto; 
        padding-bottom: 20px;
    }
    .about-content img {
            height: 40vh;
    }
    .about-content h1 {
            font-size: 24px;
            padding: 10px 0;
    }
    .founder-container {
        flex-direction: column;
        height: auto; 
        margin-top: 2rem;
    }
    .founder-content {
        width: 90%;
        height: auto; 
        margin: 15px auto;
        padding-bottom: 20px;
    }
    .founder-content img {
            height: 50vh;
    }
    .footer-container {
        height: auto;
        padding: 30px 10px;
        margin-top: 3rem;
    }
    }
</style>

<!--header section-->
<div class="header-container">
        <!--menu link-->
        @Html.Partial("_menu")
        <h1>About Us</h1>
</div>

<!--company history section-->
<div class="about-history">
    <div class="about-content">
        <h1>We are North West's best recommended chilli company</h1>
        <p>Chabis Hotness (Pty) Limited, is a company that started in 2018 and officially registered in 2019. It produces and sells Chillie Garnish Sauces. Do allow us to add some flavour and exotic taste to your foods, through our products Chabis Hotness Chillie peppers. These little bombshells of hotness flavour and spices, from the mild to the wild are the key ingredients in our products, farmed and harvested locally in South Africa, Limpopo, Gauteng and North West province farmers. We use one of the seething methods which has a very beneficial preservative that eliminates any bacterial growth (e.g. listeria) and contamination. The product has gone through microbiological, laboratory testing and has been approved to have a shelf life of 6months from date of opening. It has an advantage of being kept at a room temperature without the necessity of refrigeration. The Chabis Hotness Chillie Garnish sauce is GS1 barcode registered. It has 2 full-time management employees (Obakeng Letshwiti and Stefan Phiri), 10 part-time workers and 10 sales agents from different towns and provinces within South Africa.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="about-content">
        <img src="/images/about us chilli.jpg"
    </div>
</div>

<!--company founder section-->
<div class="founder-container">
    <div class="founder-content">
        <h1 align="center">The face of the company</h1>
        <p>Well, well, well! Are you loving our Hotness already? Let’s take you on a short-right preview about the founder…<br><br>She is young, vibrant, ambitious, resilient, and goal-oriented, with expertise in Procurement, Sourcing, Commercial, Purchasing, Contracting, and Supply Chain Management. A businesswoman through and through, she embodies fierceness, confidence, and enthusiasm. Her brand, Chabis Hotness (Pty) Ltd, reflects her dynamic personality and unwavering drive. The name 'Chabi' is derived from her own name, Mmadichaba, which means 'Mother of Nations,' symbolizing her nurturing spirit and leadership. Hailing from the sophisticated village of Moruleng, near Sun City in the North West province, she was raised by her late father, Ntsowe Joseph Molate, a man renowned for his courage and prominence, and her mother, Naome Seronamang Molate (née Letshwiti), a beautiful, prayerful, and warm-hearted woman. Both parents were successful entrepreneurs, leaving behind a legacy of resilience and achievement. Her journey is not just one of personal success but also a testament to the values of integrity, dedication, and innovation that she upholds. Committed to making a meaningful impact within her industry and community, she actively engages in initiatives that support local talent and foster sustainable practices. Through her work and brand, she aims to inspire others to embrace their potential and pursue their dreams with passion and purpose. As she continues to break barriers and set new standards, her story serves as a powerful reminder of the strength and resilience that define true leadership. In honor of her parents and their enduring influence, we take a moment of silence to remember and celebrate their lasting impact on her life and business.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="founder-content">
        <img src="/images/the founder.jpg" />
    </div>
</div>

<!--footer section-->
<div class="footer-container">
    <h2>About Us</h2>
    <p>
        Chabis Hotness,<br />
        Stirring up bold flavors and fiery passion in every jar—taste the difference with our chillies..
    </p>
    <div class="footer-icons">
        <a href="https://www.facebook.com/mmadichabasharolmolate" target="_blank">
            <i class="fa-brands fa-facebook"></i>
        </a>
        <a href="https://www.instagram.com/chabis.hotness" target="_blank">
            <i class="fa-brands fa-instagram"></i>
        </a>
        <a href="https://wa.me/+27625805348" target="_blank">
            <i class="fa-brands fa-whatsapp"></i>
        </a>
    </div>
    <p>copyright <i class="fa fa-copyright" style="font-size:15px;color:#ffffff;"></i> 2025, Chabis Hotness | Created by SyreTech SOLUTIONS</p>
</div>
